plicants><inventors><inventor sequence="00" designation="us-only"><addressbook><last-name>Barker</last-name><first-name>Jason W.</first-name><address><city>San Lorenzo</city><state>CA</state><country>US</country></address></addressbook></inventor></inventors></us-parties></us-bibliographic-data-application><abstract id="abstract"><p id="p-0001" num="0000">A first voucher, at a price that is equal to a full discounted price of a merchandise or service being offered, is provided to a computing device that is associated with a first user and that is configured to display such first voucher on a display of such computing device. The first voucher is provided from a platform that is configured to provide a plurality of vouchers from a plurality of different merchants. After the first user purchases the first voucher at the voucher purchase price, a reward, which is obtained from a portion or all of proceeds obtained from users who buy the first voucher or from another source, is remitted to the first user based on said first user's purchase of two or more of the plurality of vouchers via the platform.</p></abstract></us-patent-application>